{
  "texts": [
    "To ensure the consistency and accuracy of the information provided, in the experiment, ChatGPT was restricted to using only the data from the manuals, avoiding any external knowledge sources.",
    "The technical implementation of this approach utilised the foundation of instructional design and the science of learning to enhance the effectiveness of the ChatGPT-facilitated training.",
    "The findings of this study hold implications for both the automotive industry and educators, suggesting practical strategies for ADAS training that can be incorporated into driver education programs, dealership demonstrations, and user manuals.",
    "As the automotive landscape shifts towards increased automation, it becomes imperative to re-evaluate our training methodologies.",
    "This study offers a novel perspective by integrating LLMs into the training process, providing a promising avenue for enhancing drivers' comprehension of ADAS functions and ensuring safer road experiences in an era of automation."
  ]
}